{"tid":1502703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實防暴成日要幫藍衫執屎，唔知會唔會想屌柒啲廢柴藍衫呢","createTime":"2019-08-24T17:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T12:42:13.000Z","uid":160912,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1564345a3c7d2669cf96e3b7818a6204db1c82c1","tid":1502703,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"好似今晚麗晶咁，無啦啦因為藍衫亂拉人搞到又比人圍，依幾個月都劇本咁濟，今日仲要執屎執到成身濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最撚柒就一定係黃大仙，要幫藍衫執屎不特止仲要比啲街坊打番轉頭，全部香港人指住黎笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二個柒既都算係上水，為左要攬個垃圾大陸佬，五十幾個藍衫好似被放狗咁保護個on9 (希望有人搵到食煙放狗圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n🐶🐶🐶<br />\n🐶🚬🐶<br />\n🐶🐶🐶<br />\n<br />\n葵芳又係無啦啦有個未來戰士要拎枝雷明燈衝出黎柒，結果又要防暴執屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他都廢撚事數，獲獲都要幫藍衫做on9決定執屎，話就話同事但比著我都想屌柒啲on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f0949d350bfedc193788c2c52b2c3e8a1adac3","tid":1502703,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"推比大家笑下先"},{"pid":"ce4c530ad77982293e5064fd0890eebfec6b1446","tid":1502703,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 